  * by the format property. The format is a
  * {@link java.util.regex.Pattern regular expression}
  * and defaults to
  * <strong>^[a-z]+(\.[a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z_0-9]*)*$</strong>.
  * </p>
  * <p>
  * The default format has been chosen to match the requirements in the
  * <a
